word_mean_info__list.difference: 通常指市区外可以通行各种机动车辆的交通干线。
指从此处通往彼处的路线、路程等。
在美国，指城市中一侧或两侧建筑物林立的大道或马路；而在英国则常指通住乡村大住宅、私人大庄园或两旁栽树的道路。
指人或兽在森林、荒野或山中踩出的小径或崎岖小道。
尤指城市中的道路，往往一侧或两侧有高大建筑物；还可指城市小镇、近郊可供人、车、马行走的平坦道路。
多指由人或动物在田间、小丘或树丛中经常走动而踩出的小路，也指公园或花园等供人走的小径。
高速公路，新词，特指为车辆快速通行而修的专线，美语为freeway或expressway。
普通用词，含义广泛，可指各种路、道或通道，也可指抽象的道路。
指连接两地间供行人或车辆使用的广阔平坦的大道，多指公路，也可用于引申意义。
在英国，多指街道两旁的人行道，而美国人常用sidewlk表示人行道。
指农村或城镇的小道或小径，也指小巷。

bilingual.source: Every year, they walked the same route.
bilingual.target: 每年，他们都走同样的路线。

bilingual.source: The Bernina Express follows a route that runs from Eastern Switzerland to Northern Italy.
bilingual.target: 伯尔尼纳快车沿着一条从瑞士东部到意大利北部的路线行驶。
我们选择了较短的路线。
公交车司机知道每一条路线。

bilingual.source: We chose to take the scenic route.
bilingual.target: 我们选择走风景优美的路线。

bilingual.source: He found a quicker route to work.
bilingual.target: 他找到了一条上班更快的路线。

bilingual.source: The river flows along a winding route.
bilingual.target: 河流沿着曲折的路线流淌。

bilingual.source: We need to find a route to escape.
bilingual.target: 我们需要找到一个逃离的路线。

bilingual.source: This route has the fewest traffic lights.
bilingual.target: 这条路线的红绿灯最少。

list.abstract: Route就是用来显示、人工添加和修改路由表项目的。大多数主机一般都是驻留在只连接一台路由器的网段上。由于只有一台路由器，因此不存在使用哪一台路由器将数据包发表到远程计算机上去的问题，该路由器的IP地址可作为该网段上所有计算机的缺省网关来输入。 但是，当网络上拥有两个或多个路由器时，你就不一定想只依赖缺省网关了。实际上你可能想让你的某些远程IP地址通过某个特定的路由器来传递，而其他的远程IP则通过另一个路由器来传递。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the best route: keep on the main road until you see Windy Castle up ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这条是最好的路线，你们只要沿着主干道，一直往前开，就能到风息堡了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh Sadness. We don't have time for this. We'll just have to go around. Take the scenic route.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢 "忧忧" ，我们已经快没时间了，我们得四处走走，按观光路线走吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, let me just get one thing. It's my backup emergency supply kit. The living room escape route doesn't pass through here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我再拿一样东西，这是我的备用应急储备包，客厅的紧急逃生路线不经过这边。

yingyinNormal.en: This is exciting. Back home, the diner on Route Four serves sushi, but it's just cut up fish sticks and a side of Uncle Ben's.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真令人激动。咱家四号公路线那的馆子也卖寿司，但他们只是把炸鱼排切碎，再配上“本恩大叔”牌速食米饭。

yingyinNormal.en: Prefer a more passive route? How about simply watching TV?
yingyinNormal.zh: 想要比较被动的方法？不如就看个电视？

yingyinNormal.en: An IED right off Route 90, three kilometers from the Jordan River.
yingyinNormal.zh: 简易爆炸装置，就在90号公路旁，距约旦河三千米处。

yingyinNormal.en: The Silk Road was an ancient trade route linking China to the Mediterranean Sea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丝绸之路是连接中国和地中海的一条古贸易通道。

yingyinNormal.en: Also check the most recent satellite images for a red pick-up in the driveway. 54-09 on route.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时搜索最新卫星图像，看谁家车道上停有红色皮卡，54-09正在赶来。

yingyinNormal.en: A delta team has been clandestinely inserted. By now, they should be en route to your position.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们暗中派遣了一支突击小队，现在他们应该往你们那去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Marine one with southpaw on board, en route to Stansted. Prep air force one for urgent departure. Copy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海军一号护送左撇子飞往史坦斯特，空军一号准备紧急起飞，完毕。

yingyinNormal.en: We do not yet know how severely the president has been wounded. He is en-route to Jefferson Memorial Hospital.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们尚不清楚总统的伤情。他正在被送往杰弗逊纪念医院。

yingyinNormal.en: You'll also find a laminated copy in your welcome packet. It's on the back of the emergency escape route diagram.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欢迎礼包里还有一份塑封过的版本，就印在紧急逃生线路图的背面。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir. Look, I don't wanna go down this route any more than you do, but at least we'll have our bases covered. Yes, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生……听着，我跟你一样也不想走这条路，但至少也算面面俱到了。是，先生。

yingyinNormal.en: My father told me he planned to expand his trade route to Sumatra and Borneo, but I don't think he was looking far enough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我父亲告诉过我，他打算把商路扩展到苏门答腊岛和婆罗洲岛，但是我认为他看得还不够远。

yingyinNormal.en: We lived about a quarter mile off Route 17, about a half-mile from the town of Greenbow, Alabama. That's in the county of Greenbow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们住在17号公路附近，距离亚拉巴马州绿茵镇约半里，这个地方属于绿茵县。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, boy, a whole dollar. Now, I can quit my paper route. So, what's in it? Doesn't matter. Half the time, he just ends up playing with the box.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈呀，整整一元大洋呢，我可以不用去送报了，里面是什么啊？根本无所谓，通常他都是隔着盒子玩[模型玩具]而已。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the backstage area where all the performers gather before heading out onto the route. And there is definitely an atmosphere of anticipation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是后台准备区，演员们出发到路上前都聚集在这里。这儿绝对有一种充满期待的气氛。

yingyinNormal.en: Then a regional control center keeps tabs on it until it reaches 10,000 feet, where the flight enters one of the 21 en route centers across the country.
yingyinNormal.zh: 区域性的控制中心会负责监管，直到飞机飞行一万英尺为止，跨越国家到达21个中途指挥中心中的一个。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a method or process leading to a specified result

examination_example.sentence: For those for whom a degree is the desired <highlight>route</highlight>, consider that this may well be the first of many.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于那些认为升学是一条理想途径的人来说，学位可能是最重要的。

examination_example.sentence: Education was no longer a secure <highlight>route</highlight> of social mobility.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 教育不再是社会流动的安全途径。

examination_example.sentence: But in the everyday practice of science, discovery frequently follows an ambiguous and complicated <highlight>route</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但在科学的日常实践中，发现往往遵循一条模棱两可而复杂的途径。

sense_info_list.en: a way that you follow to get from one place to another

examination_example.sentence: When we travel down a well-known <highlight>route</highlight>, because we don't have to concentrate much, time seems to flow more quickly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我们沿着一条熟悉的路线行驶时，因为我们不需要太集中精力，时间似乎过得更快。

examination_example.sentence: Think about driving a <highlight>route</highlight> that's very familiar.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 想象一下在一条非常熟悉的路线上开车。

examination_example.sentence: This is the well-travelled road effect: People tend to underestimate the time it takes to travel a familiar <highlight>route</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是广为人知的道路效应:人们往往会低估在熟悉的道路上行驶所花费的时间。

sense_info_list.en: used before the number of a main road in the US

word_usage.usage:
the route to sth. 意为“……的途径或渠道”，如：
the route to success   成功之路 
the route to happiness 通往幸福之路

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 常指较远的路线，可能包括若干段路程。
常指溪流、天体等自然形成的轨道。
指各种道路，有时指大道，用途最广。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

sense_info_list.en:
a way that you follow to get from one place to another;
send or direct along a specified course

examination_example.sentence: The fastest evacuation <highlight>route</highlight> was through river rapids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最快的疏散路线是穿过急流。

examination_example.sentence: They are a technological leap, transporting iron ore along <highlight>routes</highlight> which run for hundreds of kilometers from mines to their destinations.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它们是一项技术飞跃，将铁矿石从矿山运输到目的地，运输路线长达数百公里。

examination_example.sentence: Birds following traditional migration <highlight>routes</highlight> were more likely to die.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 遵循传统迁徙路线的鸟类更容易死亡。

examination_example.sentence: Migrating birds affect ecosystems both at home and at their winter destinations, and disrupting the traditional <highlight>routes</highlight> could have unexpected side effects.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 迁徙的鸟类会影响目前所在地及其冬季目的地的生态系统，破坏传统路线可能会带来意想不到的副作用。

examination_example.sentence: "I followed my <highlight>route</highlight> like I normally do," Smith told a reporter.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 史密斯告诉记者：“我像往常一样沿着我的路线走。”

examination_example.sentence: The fastest <highlight>route</highlight> will take us 15.3 minutes. Should I take it?

examination_example.sentence: As soon as it's safe enough to be outside, couriers (邮递员) start distributing accumulated mail on the still-accessible <highlight>routes</highlight>.
